Package com.ibm.streams.management.domain

Interface ZooKeeperNodeMXBean

public interface ZooKeeperNodeMXBean
ZooKeeperNodeMXBean provides attributes for retrieving details about a ZooKeeper server node.

ObjectNameBuilder.zooKeeperNode(String, String, String) can be used to build the ObjectName for a ZooKeeperNodeMXBean.

Notifications:
A ZooKeeperNodeMXBean supports sending the following notifications when ZooKeeperEnsembleMXBean.refreshZooKeeperNodeBeans() is called:

javax.management.AttributeChangeNotification.ATTRIBUTE_CHANGE
